# Multiplayer (optional). Copy to `.env` and fill in from your Supabase project.
# Only Realtime is used — no tables — so the free tier is plenty. When these are
# ABSENT the Multiplayer menu is hidden and the solo game is unaffected.
#
# Uses Supabase's NEW API keys (Project → Settings → API Keys):
#   - PUBLISHABLE key `sb_publishable_...`  → client-safe, goes here.
#   - SECRET key      `sb_secret_...`       → server-only. DO NOT put it here:
#     VITE_* vars are inlined into the shipped browser bundle, which would leak
#     it. This client-only app never needs the secret key.
#
# On Vercel: add the same vars under Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# (baked in at build time — redeploy after a change). For Electron, set them in
# the shell before `npm run dist`.

VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=
